OL,3,CThe Isle of Wight Festival in numbers
OL,5,FLewis Capaldi, Calvin Harris and The
OL,6,FCure will be hitting the main stage at
OL,7,Fthe Isle of Wight Festival this
OL,8,Fweekend and organisers are hoping 2026
OL,9,Fwill be one of the best yet.
OL,11,FThe event is taking place at Seaclose
OL,12,FPark in Newport and it's the 24th
OL,13,Fedition to take place on the island.
OL,15,FThe festival was relaunched in 2002 by
OL,16,Fmusic promoter John Giddings.
OL,18,FSince then, acts to have appeared
OL,19,Finclude David Bowie, Bruce
OL,20,FSpringsteen, Paul McCartney, The
OL,21,FRolling Stones and Coldplay.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
