OL,3,CThe Isle of Wight Festival in numbers
OL,5,F400 acts are due to perform across the
OL,6,F180 acre site.
OL,8,FIn addition to Lewis Capaldi, Calvin
OL,9,FHarris and The Cure, other acts
OL,10,Fperforming at this year's festival
OL,11,Finclude the Sex Pistols featuring
OL,12,FFrank Carter, rock band The Last
OL,13,FDinner Party and US singer Teddy Swims.
OL,15,FLocal acts are also represented, with
OL,16,FWet Leg, who are from the Island, also
OL,17,Fperforming.
OL,19,FThe indie rock band first appeared at
OL,20,Fthe festival in 2019.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
