OL,3,CThe Isle of Wight Festival in numbers
OL,5,FThe festival runs from 18 June to 21
OL,6,FJune.
OL,8,FLewis Capaldi is headlining on Friday
OL,9,F(19 June) and Calvin Harris is doing
OL,10,Flikewise on Saturday, with The Cure
OL,11,Fbringing the festival to a close on
OL,12,FSunday.
OL,14,FTickets for the event are sold out,
OL,15,Fwith hot weather forecast throughout
OL,16,Fthe weekend.
